<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Advert Created</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 5px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .button.reject {
            background-color: #dc3545;
        }
        .button.reject:hover {
            background-color: #bd2130;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h2>Advert Created</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>We are pleased to inform you that an advert titled "<strong>{{ advert.title }}</strong>" has been created and is awaiting review.</p>
        <p>Description of the advert:</p>
        <blockquote>
            {{ advert.context }}
        </blockquote>
        <p>Please choose an action for this advert:</p>
        <p>
            <a href="{{ url('app_advert_show', {'id': advert.id}) }}" class="button">View Advert</a>
            <a href="{{ url('app_advert_publish', {'id': advert.id}) }}" class="button">Publish Advert</a>
            <a href="{{ url('app_advert_reject', {'id': advert.id}) }}" class="button reject">Reject Advert</a>
        </p>
        <p>Lebonplan.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply directly.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>

